# Force LF for shell scripts, git hooks, and the extensionless `edda` launcher —
# they must run via bash on Windows; CRLF breaks the shebang ("bad interpreter").
*.sh text eol=lf
.githooks/* text eol=lf
.claude/tools/edda text eol=lf

# Edda source + compiler-emitted structure maps: LF.
*.ea text eol=lf
*.toon text eol=lf
